"{\"uid\": \"article217\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Nang' (the main shareholder), asked Wang She to leave the company definitively.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 79, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is quite shocking as it's like a new shareholder asking the boss of Virgin to leave his company!\", \"from\": 80, \"to\": 181, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is now at the forefront of every business conversation, and has become like a reality show with everyone wanting to know what is going to happen.\", \"from\": 182, \"to\": 332, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There were a lot of conversations on Chinese social media surrounding this topic, and how unfair this is towards such a great leader.\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 466, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nobody really knows what will happen, but we should find out very soon!\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 538, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The early predictions are that he will be fired from his company.\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 604, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"China resents the oblivion of a part of their population: the working class  The HotPost of the week is a photo documentary about really hard workers in a metal factory.\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's about the lives of these people who are pretty old, who's work consists of carrying the raw materials to make metal.\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 897, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's almost like modern slavery in a way, because the conditions are so incredibly tough.\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 987, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They have to move approximately 300 tons every day, and are paid only 60 cent RMB per ton, making about 200 RMB every day which is about 3 euro per day.\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Their living and working conditions are just shocking!\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1195, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The documentary is very emotional and shows the gap between the modern and digital forward-thinking Tier 1 Chinese cities and this other China in the countryside.\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1358, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot of people were extremely touched by this documentary and felt a lot of empathy towards the workers.\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1465, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Especially people from Tier 1 cities who cannot believe that this is still happening in 2016, calling on the government to act and help these people.\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1615, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a way, the documentary was very useful, by showing the plight of these workers and generating engagement, generating 234,000 retweets on Sina Weibo, and 200,000 likes.\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1786, \"entities\": []}]}"